Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.58,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:24.33,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:31.01,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:38.01,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.97,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:44.52,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:49.44,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.65,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:57.07,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:03.12,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.67,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.04,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:18.39,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,The mysterious and vast universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,In this universe exists the evil life forms, \Nthe space pirates Geisters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,who've invaded Earth in order to obtain the treasures of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,However, in front of the Geisters who use destruction and plunder as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,a hero appeared, who completely stood in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,He is the cosmic police, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is the story of Brave Exkaiser and his friends, who fight against evil all around the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:18.48,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.168,313.2)}Time Is a Mess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.6\pos(252.632,124.4)}Great Treasure Exhibition 13F         Summer Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan is so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the Anniversary of Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable that she's late on the Anniversary of Sky Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2:30 we'll watch a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at 4 we'll have tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and at 5 it's study time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My perfect schedule is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you made a too \Ndetailed time schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be like me and just be like "At afternoon it's playing time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a man who carries Japan on his shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could make a loose schedule like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of what to wear so I came a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! About 30 minutes don't even feel like we waited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are one to talk!\N You were angry just a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an atomic clock that shows the standard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the world, people match their country's time to this atomic clock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they can show the exact time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The world's time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyuuku department store's mechanism clock disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It was the flower clock that \Ndisappeared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the mechanism clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find that out by reading papa's newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to wait for the evening paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Today afternoon, starting from the atomic clock of world's standard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,incidents where rare clocks were stolen from all over the world happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapporo's clock tower and London's Big Ben are both now lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't only the mechanic clock that disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,According to witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,they've said that a dinosaur took them, but there's no positive proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Rare clocks are being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, since there's a rare clock here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll dash through a second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Thunder Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dash Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just slipped a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those damn Geisters ruined our race again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'll come immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat them up easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I, Dash Max, exist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your evil doings are absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max, answer! Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a payback from the other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the time before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stop soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't be much of a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more important now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can sell this much rare \Nclocks at a high price!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I stole most of them, \Nso my share must be the biggest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll obviously get the best share, \Nsince I'm the one who thought of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even worked that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me-...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the fighting among yourselves for later and look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Installation of the spare atomic clock has been finished successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, all the clocks around the world have regained the standard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who was it that said that there's only one atomic clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could know there's a spare one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they're playing dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The clocks would be a treasure, \Nif there's only one of them in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no treasure if two of them exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,... Is what Lord Dino Geist said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to make the other clocks out of order, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This place was safe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're only stealing clocks... Could it be because today's the Anniversary of Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mechanic clock of the Kyuuku department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But that couldn't be... Since it got stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, if it isn't the atomic clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the clock museum, \Nit's got everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastards! Don't think you'll get off easy for doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you still want us to pay attention to you! There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Ptera Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapporo's clock tower and other \Nvarious tourist places-...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry for that. We'll continue the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This piece of news seems to tell something about that recent shock wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like clocks have broken all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I flew in a 5 km radius around the race area, but I didn't get any response.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Blue Raker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I went as far as 20 km from the race area, but I couldn't catch a response from Dash Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the clocks in the world broke at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the work of Geisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spare atomic clock is broken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the exact time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When is the 18:00 train arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the 17:00 train hasn't arrived yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on with that 17:00 train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I don't know which trains are running at the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the 3 o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie! What do you mean "3 o'clock news"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already dark outside! It's nighttime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better show our drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The 3 o'clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,news...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Aiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor, this is all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why we became so busy when there's no clocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Get the manuscripts printed quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief editor, I am getting paid for overtime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time to think about useless things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here... The classes were longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They were actually shorter than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that tree's shadow \Nis currently in that position...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's 3 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the theory of the sun watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned it in grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from Mr. Tokuda, you are so educated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on now, madam! Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's expand the scope of our search.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Raker should head west as till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Raker should head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a mess now that the clocks are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't clocks only machines that punctuate time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So why all this just because such things broke...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that clocks are gone, I realized for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that punctuating time is really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know the punctuation, \Nyou just keep on studying or working
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what makes you tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So clocks are very important, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And those Geisters dare mess with such important things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Blue Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, I've caught an unidentified energy wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get rid of those rare clocks already and make Lord Dino Geist delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It's about the time I'll get contacted by the space merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet those humans have now learned the dread of us Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the only time you'll be able to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll laugh as much as I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you take our capture so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My captures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash Max! Thank god you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't stop with just stealing clocks from around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so you dared to steal time from humans \Nand disrupt the peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the stolen clocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max, Drill Max! You two should protect Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Blue Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Green Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Raker Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Left&Right Fusion, Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Chain Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Blaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you learned your lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine and I'll aid too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible in your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team, Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Fusion, God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,God Cosmic Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, let's retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The clocks are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was Exkaiser and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta, feel at ease. \NThe time has returned to you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon at 15:05, the various clocks around the country
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have returned to normal \Nsimultaneously for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the next news,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the clocks that were stolen around the world were found in faraway mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, the morning paper came only now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's this thick! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It's just that... How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's good that everything solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You were fine even without a clock, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine even if there's no clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but if there's no clock then papa gets busy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best when there's a clock and papa is right next to me. Right, papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.98,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:05.07,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:15.12,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:22.75,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:31.05,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:39.06,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:45.89,NextEpisodePreview,,0,0,0,,{\pos(312.512,306.667)}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, blue, yellow, purple and... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't say all 7 colors, \Nrainbows are really pretty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going on a hiking to the \NRainbow Waterfall today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But even Geisters came along with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible! The dam's water is overflowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The town will be filled with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.98,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Flood at the Rainbow Waterfall
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an alien in your home, too?
